<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 07 at 6:57AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Slippery Conditions Possible Early this Morning...
Patchy light freezing drizzle was developing and will continue
through 9 AM before mixing to light snow. A thin glaze of ice may
develop on primarily untreated and elevated surfaces, including
bridges and overpasses. If traveling early this morning, remain
alert for changing road conditions and allow extra time to reach
your destination.</description>
